Good luck.

107
00:05:54,396 --> 00:05:57,232
Keep in touch.

108
00:05:58,816 --> 00:06:00,277
Good luck. Have a good day.

109
00:06:01,444 --> 00:06:03,280
-I'm off.
-Bye.

110
00:06:08,911 --> 00:06:10,245
I'm off.

111
