INTRO

117
00:07:09,930 --> 00:07:13,141
-It's better when it's bigger.
-Really?

118
00:07:13,225 --> 00:07:15,768
-The pop-up opens on the 10th?
-The 10th.

119
00:07:15,852 --> 00:07:18,021
-Can I come?
-Come! Of course.

120
00:07:18,105 --> 00:07:20,065
Okay, I'll come.

121
00:07:20,148 --> 00:07:24,194
Having someone to collaborate with
on Terrace House...

122
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:27,655
I was hoping for that.

123
00:07:28,281 --> 00:07:29,907
-You're glad?
-I'm really glad.

124
00:07:29,992 --> 00:07:31,701
I'm glad, but...

125
00:07:36,081 --> 00:07:37,874
It's so quiet now.

126
00:07:37,958 --> 00:07:40,543
No one's home when I get back.

127
00:07:40,627 --> 00:07:45,673
Not to further put a damper or anything...

128
00:07:47,342 --> 00:07:53,056
but now that we've collaborated
and the pop-up is opening...

129
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:56,684
I've finished what I set out to do.

130
00:07:57,978 --> 00:08:00,981
So after this...

131
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:03,775
I'm leaving.

132
00:08:08,989 --> 00:08:12,659
I think there'll be more opportunities...

133
00:08:13,410 --> 00:08:15,870
once I open the pop-up.

134
00:08:15,953 --> 00:08:17,914
-And you'll have your café?
-Yes.

135
00:08:17,998 --> 00:08:20,833
-You're going to open one in Tokyo, too?
-Yes.

136
00:08:20,917 --> 00:08:24,712
I'm sure we'll work together again
in the future.

137
00:08:25,297 --> 00:08:26,339
Yeah.

138
00:08:27,507 --> 00:08:31,844
I was hoping to meet someone
who would inspire me.

139
00:08:31,928 --> 00:08:33,930
So I'm really glad I met you.

140
00:08:34,014 --> 00:08:35,890
I'm glad I met you, too.

141
00:08:35,973 --> 00:08:39,019
You're probably
the easiest member to talk to.

142
00:08:39,102 --> 00:08:40,770
-Really?
-Yeah.

143
00:08:40,853 --> 00:08:42,105
That makes me happy.

144
00:08:44,941 --> 00:08:47,069
It's been really fun.

145
00:08:47,152 --> 00:08:49,279
It really has been...

146
00:08:49,362 --> 00:08:50,655
this experience.

147
