-Yeah.

240
00:15:21,963 --> 00:15:24,466
-Are you full?
-We ate a lot.

241
00:15:31,681 --> 00:15:32,724
How much?

242
00:15:33,766 --> 00:15:34,601
I have...

243
00:15:42,859 --> 00:15:43,860
Seriously.

244
00:15:43,943 --> 00:15:45,987
Seriously, seriously, seriously.

245
00:15:52,577 --> 00:15:53,578
